---
const now = new Date().toLocaleString('fr-FR');
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Decap OAuth Service</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        background: #0b1120;
        color: #e2e8f0;
        font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      }

      main {
        width: min(720px, calc(100vw - 48px));
        padding: 32px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: rgba(21, 30, 50, 0.9);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      code {
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Service OAuth Decap</h1>
      <p>Ce projet Vercel sert uniquement les routes <code>/oauth</code> et <code>/oauth/callback</code> pour l’administration du blog.</p>
      <p>Il ne doit pas être indexé ni utilisé comme site public principal.</p>
      <p>Dernier rendu local : {now}</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
